name: PunkRock Romance -  XIX I Put a Spell on You
description:
PunkRock Romance Girls Part II

I put a pink candle and a rose under my bed, wrote a sweet letter and whispered your name.
The magic blue moon tells me in my ears that your mind and heart are mine, and you have no choice, sorry baby now and forever you belong to me.
